  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic and cook until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add tempeh and cook until lightly browned, about 4-5 minutes.",
    "Stir in curry powder and garam masala and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add curry sauce and coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let cook for 10-15 minutes or until sauce has thickened.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
